# =============================================================================
# notifications.http — RESQID Super Admin
# Notification module — all 3 endpoints
#
# Setup:
#   1. Install REST Client extension (VS Code) or use JetBrains HTTP Client
#   2. Run login request first → copy token → paste into @token below
#   3. Replace @baseUrl if your dev port differs
# =============================================================================

@baseUrl    = http://localhost:3000
@token      = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@authHeader = Bearer {{token}}

# Replace these with real UUIDs from your DB after seeding
@schoolId        = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@notificationId  = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002


# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AUTH — run once, copy token from response
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Login as Super Admin
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/super-admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "superadmin@resqid.in",
  "password": "YourPassword@123"
}

###


# =============================================================================
# 1. STATS
#    GET /api/super-admin/notifications/stats
#    → Powers the three stat cards:
#      "Total Notifications" / "Avg. Delivery Rate" / "Total Failed"
# =============================================================================

### 1a. Stats — default (last 30 days)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications/stats
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 1b. Stats — last 24 hours
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications/stats?date_range=24h
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 1c. Stats — last 7 days
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications/stats?date_range=7d
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 1d. Stats — this calendar month
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications/stats?date_range=this_month
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 1e. Stats — custom date range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications/stats?date_range=custom&date_from=2026-01-01&date_to=2026-03-31
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 1f. Stats — VALIDATION ERROR (custom without date_from/date_to)
# Expected: 422 Validation Error
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications/stats?date_range=custom
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###


# =============================================================================
# 2. LIST NOTIFICATIONS
#    GET /api/super-admin/notifications
#    → Powers the Notification Logs table with filters + pagination
# =============================================================================

### 2a. List — no filters, first page (default limit 10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2b. List — page 2, limit 25
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?page=2&limit=25
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2c. List — filter by channel: PUSH
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?channel=PUSH
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2d. List — filter by channel: EMAIL
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?channel=EMAIL
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2e. List — filter by channel: SMS
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?channel=SMS
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2f. List — filter by status: SENT
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?status=SENT
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2g. List — filter by status: FAILED
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?status=FAILED
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2h. List — filter by status: QUEUED
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?status=QUEUED
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2i. List — filter by status: SUPPRESSED
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?status=SUPPRESSED
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2j. List — filter by type: SCAN_ALERT
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?type=SCAN_ALERT
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2k. List — filter by type: BILLING_ALERT
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?type=BILLING_ALERT
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2l. List — filter by type: SCAN_ANOMALY
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?type=SCAN_ANOMALY
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2m. List — filter by type: CARD_EXPIRING
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?type=CARD_EXPIRING
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2n. List — filter by type: CARD_REVOKED
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?type=CARD_REVOKED
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2o. List — filter by type: CARD_REPLACED
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?type=CARD_REPLACED
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2p. List — filter by school
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?school_id={{schoolId}}
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2q. List — combined: school + channel + status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?school_id={{schoolId}}&channel=PUSH&status=FAILED
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2r. List — combined: type + status + date_range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?type=SCAN_ALERT&status=SENT&date_range=7d
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2s. List — combined: all filters together
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?school_id={{schoolId}}&type=SCAN_ALERT&channel=PUSH&status=FAILED&date_range=30d&page=1&limit=25
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2t. List — custom date range with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?date_range=custom&date_from=2026-02-01&date_to=2026-03-07&page=1&limit=50
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2u. List — VALIDATION ERROR: limit over max (100)
# Expected: 422 Validation Error
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?limit=200
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2v. List — VALIDATION ERROR: invalid channel value
# Expected: 422 Validation Error
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?channel=WHATSAPP_BUSINESS
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2w. List — VALIDATION ERROR: invalid status value
# Expected: 422 Validation Error
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?status=DELIVERED
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2x. List — VALIDATION ERROR: invalid school_id (not UUID)
# Expected: 422 Validation Error
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?school_id=not-a-uuid
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2y. List — VALIDATION ERROR: custom range missing date_to
# Expected: 422 Validation Error
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications?date_range=custom&date_from=2026-01-01
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 2z. List — AUTH ERROR: no token
# Expected: 401 Unauthorized
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications

###


# =============================================================================
# 3. SINGLE NOTIFICATION (Payload Modal)
#    GET /api/super-admin/notifications/:id
#    → Called when user clicks [View Payload] in the table row
# =============================================================================

### 3a. Get notification by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications/{{notificationId}}
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 3b. NOT FOUND — valid UUID but no record
# Expected: 404 Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 3c. VALIDATION ERROR — id is not a UUID
# Expected: 422 Validation Error
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications/not-a-uuid
Authorization: {{authHeader}}

###

### 3d. AUTH ERROR — no token
# Expected: 401 Unauthorized
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/super-admin/notifications/{{notificationId}}

###
